com.microsoft.azure.management.sql

Class FirewallRuleOperationsImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.microsoft.azure.management.sql.FirewallRuleOperationsImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FirewallRuleOperations, ServiceOperations<SqlManagementClientImpl>

    public class FirewallRuleOperationsImpl
extends Object
implements ServiceOperations<SqlManagementClientImpl>, FirewallRuleOperations
    Represents all the operations for operating on Azure SQL Database Server Firewall Rules. Contains operations to: Create, Retrieve, Update, and Delete firewall rules.
